Rui,

15
00:01:07,150 --> 00:01:08,120
ever since I came back,

16
00:01:08,120 --> 00:01:09,350
you've been following me.

17
00:01:09,350 --> 00:01:10,950
Can you give me some time alone?

18
00:01:11,310 --> 00:01:12,310
Sorry, Miss Su.

19
00:01:12,480 --> 00:01:13,840
Mr. Xiao asked me to stay by your side at all times.

20
00:01:14,710 --> 00:01:15,400
Even so,

21
00:01:15,400 --> 00:01:17,120
