22
00:01:21,510 --> 00:01:22,280
Step aside.

23
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:24,510
Miss Su, please don't make things difficult for me.

24
00:01:24,510 --> 00:01:25,150
I really can't do it.

25
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:31,200
Xiao Lang neither lets me go out

26
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:32,310
nor allows me to work,

27
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:36,760
and he has you follow me every day.

28
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:38,430
Is he up to something?

29
00:01:38,710 --> 00:01:39,590
I have no idea.

30
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:43,280
Fine.

31
00:01:43,840 --> 00:01:45,120
Then I'll go for a walk in the garden.

32
00:01:51,200 --> 00:01:51,870
Xiao Lang.

33
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,360
You're back.

34
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:50,910
Let me tell you.

35
00:02:51,310 --> 00:02:52,520
When I was little,

36
00:02:52,710 --> 00:02:54,520
after we moved here,

37
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:57,120
I would often sit here waiting for you.

38
00:02:57,710 --> 00:03:00,710
Every single day, I would watch that entrance,

39
00:03:00,870 --> 00:03:02,400
and whenever I saw a child passing by,

40
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:03,870
I would think it was you coming back.

41
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:06,000
I'd happily run over,

42
00:03:07,910 --> 00:03:09,470
only to find out it wasn't you.

43
00:03:13,310 --> 00:03:14,310
I promise

44
00:03:16,150 --> 00:03:17,000
I'll come back to you

45
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:18,960
as soon as I get off work.

46
00:03:22,710 --> 00:03:24,400
You're only going to get busier

47
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:26,710
and keep working late.

48
00:03:26,710 --> 00:03:27,520
In case you think otherwise,

49
00:03:27,710 --> 00:03:28,710
I'm not waiting for you.

50
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:32,840
Don't worry, it'll be over soon.

51
00:03:33,430 --> 00:03:35,030
Once I find evidence of Gao Rui's crimes

52
00:03:35,030 --> 00:03:36,030
and kick her out of the company,

53
00:03:37,190 --> 00:03:38,360
everything will be settled.

54
00:03:39,910 --> 00:03:41,120
Then, we'll go on a trip

55
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:43,120
to see the lavender fields in Provence,

56
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:44,710
the Northern Lights in Iceland,

57
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:47,150
and the Bridge of Sighs in Venice

58
00:03:47,150 --> 00:03:48,240
before it disappears.

59
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:51,840
All right.

60
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:13,290
Who are you?

61
00:04:13,870 --> 00:04:15,210
