66
00:04:47,510 --> 00:04:50,680
How dare a mere maid like you barge into my house?

67
00:04:52,510 --> 00:04:54,830
From now on, this is my house.

68
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:56,830
You didn't know, did you?

69
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:59,630
