73
00:05:05,950 --> 00:05:07,360
is now mine.

74
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:08,160
Nonsense!

75
00:05:08,830 --> 00:05:10,360
How could you possibly have that much money?

76
00:05:12,390 --> 00:05:15,950
Are you in cahoots with Xiao Lang?

77
00:05:17,190 --> 00:05:18,680
What's your relationship with him?

78
00:05:21,070 --> 00:05:23,920
Xiao Lang is the person you pushed into the river all those years ago.

79
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:34,310
Li Zixing?

80
00:05:38,310 --> 00:05:39,720
You didn't see this coming, did you?

81
00:05:40,270 --> 00:05:41,720
I saved him.

82
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:44,360
I couldn't save Miss Meizhen,

83
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:48,040
but I did save her son.

84
00:05:48,510 --> 00:05:49,920
We've returned this time

85
00:05:50,070 --> 00:05:52,000
to take back everything you and Su Qichao

86
00:05:52,310 --> 00:05:54,240
stole back then.

87
00:05:58,870 --> 00:06:00,310
Everything we stole?

88
00:06:03,190 --> 00:06:05,120
No wonder the moment Xiao Lang returned,

89
00:06:06,070 --> 00:06:09,190
he seized all of Su Qichao's assets

90
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:11,390
and drove him to his death.

91
00:06:13,770 --> 00:06:15,950
Su Qichao,

92
00:06:16,390 --> 00:06:18,190
after over a decade,

93
00:06:18,950 --> 00:06:20,720
the very person you tried so hard to save

94
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:24,070
only sees you as his enemy after coming back.

95
00:06:26,750 --> 00:06:27,720
Su Qichao,

96
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:30,390
now that you're buried underground,

97
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:32,310
can you see this clearly?

98
00:06:35,060 --> 00:06:36,310
What do you mean?

99
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:43,130
Didn't you and Su Qichao

100
00:06:43,310 --> 00:06:45,140
conspire to harm Miss Meizhen?

101
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:50,000
I was the one who killed Shao Meizhen.

102
00:06:53,510 --> 00:06:54,190
Gao Rui,

103
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:55,400
please spare my son and me.

104
00:06:55,510 --> 00:06:56,560
You already have my husband,

105
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:57,800
and I've agreed to give you the house and the company.

106
00:06:57,800 --> 00:06:59,240
How could I possibly leave any loose ends?

107
00:06:59,360 --> 00:07:01,120
Everything belongs to me now.

108
00:07:01,310 --> 00:07:02,390
I want you dead!

109
00:07:02,510 --> 00:07:04,630
I want both you and your son dead!

110
00:07:05,040 --> 00:07:06,750
If you dare lay a finger on my son,

111
00:07:06,830 --> 00:07:08,190
I'll haunt you even in death!

112
00:07:08,390 --> 00:07:10,120
Then go ahead and die!

113
00:07:12,190 --> 00:07:14,270
Mom, I'm back!

114
00:07:16,750 --> 00:07:17,360
Mom.

115
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:20,610
Wake up.

116
00:07:20,630 --> 00:07:21,270
Mom.

117
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:22,630
Mom.

118
00:07:23,510 --> 00:07:24,190
- Ms. Shao! - Mom.

119
00:07:32,630 --> 00:07:33,430
Gao Rui,

120
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,390
