121
00:07:35,510 --> 00:07:36,950
This is murder!

122
00:07:41,610 --> 00:07:42,720
Shao Meizhen's death

123
00:07:42,720 --> 00:07:44,120
benefits you the most.

124
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:45,360
Su Qichao,

125
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:49,270
if you want a share of the company too,

126
00:07:49,270 --> 00:07:50,720
